### KrtBank API - Testes HTTP

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000
@apiVersion = v1

### 1. Obter todas as contas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contas
Accept: application/json

### 2. Obter conta por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contas/{{contaId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Criar nova conta
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeTitular": "João Silva Santos",
  "cpf": "123.456.789-00"
}

### 4. Atualizar conta
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/contas/{{contaId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeTitular": "João Silva Santos Atualizado"
}

### 5. Ativar conta
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/contas/{{contaId}}/ativar
Accept: application/json

### 6. Inativar conta
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/contas/{{contaId}}/inativar
Accept: application/json

### 7. Remover conta
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/contas/{{contaId}}
Accept: application/json

### 8. Swagger UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger
Accept: text/html